      "text": "Third consecutive first-trimester pregnancy loss. Fetal pole growth arrest at approximately 7 weeks 1 day with absent cardiac activity on 8-week follow-up transvaginal ultrasound. D&C performed 2025-03-12. Cytogenetic analysis of POC revealed normal female karyotype (46,XX), eliminating embryonic aneuploidy as the cause."
